These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: disco, soul
There are 2 different nationalities: italian, turkish
There are 2 different favourite colors: green, apricot
1. the person who likes apricot is on the left or right of the turkish##3
2. the person drinking fanta is in an even position##4
3. the fan of soul is the person drinking coffee##1
4. the person who likes apricot is on the right of the person who likes green##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Beverage      | coffee  | fanta   |
| Music-Genre   | soul     | disco   |
| Nationality         | turkish | italian |
| Color     | green | apricot    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
2 different games are played: poker, mah-jongg
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, game
2 different pets are kept: dog, rat
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: sunflower, tulip
1. the owner of the rat is in an odd position##4
2. the oliveros-smoker is the person who growstulip##1
3. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the game-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Game          | poker     | mah-jongg |
| Cigar   | game | oliveros  |
| Pet           | rat         | dog     |
| Flower     | sunflower   | tulip    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: d&b, metal
2 different games are played: mah-jongg, domino
There 2 different types of food: raspberry, cauliflower
The people use 2 different means of transport: bike, helicopter
1. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the person playing domino##3
2. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the person playing domino##1
3. the fan of d&b is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| Music-Genre    | metal     | d&b |
| Game         | domino | mah-jongg    |
| Food         | raspberry         | cauliflower        |
| Transport   | bike         | helicopter    |

