.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-4::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: soccer, handball
There are 2 different favourite colors: red, grey
The people have 2 different hobbies: card-games, cooking
The people have 2 different jobs:  designer, teacher
1. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
2. the person who likes grey is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
3. the teacher is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Sport      | handball     | soccer |
| Color          | grey   | red  |
| Hobby         | card-games | cooking     |
| Job   | designer  | teacher         |

