2 different pets are kept: chinchilla, frog
1. the american is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
2. the owner of the frog is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's birthday is in september is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |
| Sport      | cricket | golf       |
| Birthday           | september      | december     |
| Nationality   | egyptian       | american   |
| Pet           | frog          | chinchilla |

