.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-6::.
There 2 different types of food: spinach, zucchini
There are 2 different nationalities: dutch, egyptian
The people have 2 different hobbies: gardening, writing
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, cain
1. the cain-smoker is in an even position##4
2. the egyptian is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person eating zucchini is the dutch##1
4. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the egyptian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
| Food           | zucchini | spinach    |
| Nationality   | dutch       | egyptian |
| Hobby           | gardening         | writing    |
| Cigar         | aristoff    | cain   |

