The people prefer 2 different music-genres: d&b, disco
1. the doctor is on the left of the person eating potato##1
2. the person eating cauliflower is on the left or right of the old-henry-smoker##3
3. the fan of d&b is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |    2     |
| Cigar    | chaman | old-henry    |
| Job         | doctor        | designer |
| Food         | cauliflower          | potato     |
| Music-Genre   | d&b        | disco     |

 